kb3.structure: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `kb3_inv_crp` ( `inc_kll_id` int(6) NOT NULL, `inc_crp_id` int(3) NOT NULL, `inc_timestamp` datetime NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`inc_kll_id`,`inc_crp_id`), KEY `inc_crp_time` (`inc_crp_id`,`inc_timestamp`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
